pinned version, its license tier, and its declared SPDX license, plus the
policies that govern how the tools are trusted and used.

The canonical machine-readable source of truth is
`.pi/skills/sca/scripts/tool_manifest.py`. This human-readable NOTICE is kept
in sync with it (a test asserts every manifest tool name appears here).

All SPDX identifiers below are DECLARED with PROBABLE confidence. They are NOT
asserted as CERTAIN in code: the authoritative source is each project's own
